Titolo: Nijiiro Dodge Ball: Otome Tachi no Seishun

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Nijiiro Dodge Ball: Otome Tachi no Seishun (Japanese: 虹色ドッジボール 乙女たちの青春, Hepburn: lit. Rainbow-colored Dodgeball: Youth of Maidens) is the second dodge ball game developed by Million and published by Atlus. The game combines elements of Super Dodge Ball with growth sim elements. Similar to Super Dodge Ball Advance, this game has no Kunio-kun characters.
A planned deluxe pack version of the game includes guide book and a set of 12 postcards, but the plan was scrapped. The items became available through early orders of the game. In addition, pre-orders through Sofmap, Messe Sanoh, Gamers receive telephone card.